cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.AI

The paper deals with temporal logics interpreted over data words with multiple attributes and their correspondences with reachability-like decision problems for counter systems. This involves concepts from logic (cs.LO), data structures (cs.DS), Petri nets (cs.PL), formal languages (cs.FL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in terms of reasoning and decision-making. Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
